steps.name: I am using Appium for device "iPhone 8" and IOS version "11.3"
I am using IOS the app directory of "/Users/steveyoung/Documents/Appium/" and app "Hargreaves Lansdown.app"
I launch the App on the IOS Device
the IOS HL Welcome screen is displayed
I IOS Take me back to the App
then I IOS swipe to the "left"
the IOS HL fingerprint or Face ID info screen is displayed
then I IOS swipe to the "left"
the IOS Quick actions info screen is displayed
then I IOS swipe to the "left"
the IOS Top up from your mobile info screen is displayed
then I IOS swipe to the "left"
the IOS New share dealing options info screen is displayed
then I click the IOS Get Started button
I view the IOS Terms & Conditions
I IOS scroll "up" the page 4 times
I IOS Select Accept
I should see the IOS Markets homepage
I enter the IOS Debug menu
I choose Stubs and Remote from the Debug menu
I click on the IOS Market Icon
I IOS Take me back to the App
I IOS pull down and refresh the page
I click on the IOS Market Icon
I IOS click on the "Xetra DAX" link
I IOS go back to the Markets page
I click on the IOS Account Icon
I click on the IOS Log in button
I enter IOS a Username of "clnt1300107"
I enter IOS a Date of Birth of "010351"
I click on the IOS Continue Log in button
I IOS Select Accept
I IOS enter the Master Password characters of "r" "d" "g"
I click on the IOS Master Password Log In
I IOS Enter the SIPP Market
I IOS accept the Got it dialogue pop-up
I IOS switch view to Prices
I IOS switch view to Details
I IOS click on Action
I IOS choose to Top up
I IOS enter a Top up amount of "25000"
I IOS click Top up Continue
I IOS choose Amend the Top Up
I IOS choose to Exit
I IOS click on Action
I IOS click on Withdraw Money
I IOS enter a Top up amount of "100"
I IOS click Top up Continue
I IOS enter a trading password of "trading123"
I IOS click on Confirm Withdrawal
I IOS should see the Withdrawal Instruction confirmation screen
I Pause for 5 seconds to debug
I IOS take a screenshot
I IOS Return to account
I click on the IOS Market Icon
I IOS click on the "FTSE 100" link
I IOS scroll "up" the page 4 times
I IOS click on the "FALLERS" link
I IOS scroll "down" the page 4 times
I IOS click on the "A-Z" link
I IOS scroll "up" the page 4 times
